    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people say \"it gets better\" or whatever but it doesn't feel like it. it's just math at this point. every month we lose more than we make. if i wasn't here, the money they spend on my food, my clothes, my car, my medical stuff... it could all go to them instead. i'm literally just a drain on their resources.",
